# Spanish Learning GUI Application

This is a graphical user interface (GUI) application built using Python and PyQt that helps users learn Spanish vocabulary and practice grammar exercises.

## Features

- Vocabulary Quiz: Test your knowledge of Spanish words and their English translations. The quiz presents random questions and provides instant feedback on your answers.

- Grammar Exercises: Practice your understanding of Spanish grammar with interactive exercises. The exercises cover various topics such as verb conjugation, sentence formation, and more.

## Prerequisites

- Python 3.9 or above
- PyQt6 library

## Installation

1. Clone the repository:
   ```
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/spanish-learning-gui.git
   ```

2. Change to the project directory:
   ```
   cd spanish-learning-gui
   ```

3. Install the required dependencies:
   ```
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   ```

## Usage

1. Run the application:
   ```
   python main.py
   ```

2. The main window of the application will appear, providing options to start the vocabulary quiz or grammar exercises.

3. Select the desired option to begin learning and practicing Spanish.

